BoxAndWhisker Chart Demo
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>
This sample demonstrates a box-and-whisker chart, which is an efficient method for displaying a five-number data summary. This chart summarizes the following statistical measures.
</Paragraph>
<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Median</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Upper and lower quartiles (75th percentile to 25th percentile)</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Minimum and maximum data values</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

