Features</Paragraph>

<List Margin="25,0,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph>Ability to display a distribution analysis with a box-and-whisker chart.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Five possible y-values: minimum, lower quartile, median, upper quartile, and maximum.</Paragraph></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph>Ability to specify multiple values for one point.</Paragraph></ListItem>

